हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Rosa and Emma enjoy an idyllic life in their inherited family castle until fate intervenes. When Rosa falls into a coma just before her wedding to the charming Edward Douglas, her sister Emma makes a fateful decision—she steps into Rosa's place at the altar. As Emma and Edward navigate their complicated relationship amid mounting challenges, the unthinkable happens: Rosa awakens after six long months. With the fragile web of lies unraveling and loyalties tested, Emma must face her sister with the devastating truth, igniting a powder keg of emotions that threatens to destroy the sisters' bond forever.
